#

Greek Lamb Burger

25 min
$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickEasyComfort Food

Description

Juicy lamb patties seasoned with fresh herbs and spices, served on a soft bun with tangy tzatziki and fresh vegetables.

Ingredients

  • ground lamb: 1 pound
  • burger buns: 4
  • tzatziki sauce: 1 cup
  • lettuce leaves: 4
  • tomato, sliced: 1
  • red onion, thinly sliced: 1
  • feta cheese, crumbled: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • fresh parsley, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
